title._content: 4-H boys receive training in soil judging

description._content: Original Collection: Extension Service Records Group Item Number: RG111:SG1 Warm Springs Range Unit 8 Image Description: Photo was from the 1961/1962 Warm Springs Extension annual report. Dick Merritt, soil scientist, trained the club members in soil judging. You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here. Want more?
